  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bring Hope &amp; Healing to 30 Vets Impacted by PTSD</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nearly 22 veterans per day commit suicide and not enough is being done understand and treat the root causes of this epidemic. At Soldier&apos;s Heart, we seek to show modern warriors that what we commonly refer to as PTSD or &quot;Post Traumatic Stress Disorder&quot; is a normal and natural response to the battle experience. It is not a pathology or a disease to be treated. All donation made will go to covering the cost of healing retreats for modern day warriors.</narrative>
  </description>
